      <h2>Our History</h2>
      <p>Founded by Reagan Otema, Rafting Adventure is based at the Source of the Nile in Jinja, Uganda. With years of experience leading thrilling white-water rafting excursions, we’re dedicated to sharing the exhilarating beauty of Uganda’s rapids with the world. Our mission is to offer unforgettable adventures that combine excitement, safety, and a deep respect for nature.</p>
